{
  "id": "RAW_84a51ab2",
  "title": "试玩 PixVerse R1 五分钟，我意识到 AI 视频不对劲了",
  "url": "https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MzIwMTU5OTQ1Nw==&mid=2653724101&idx=1&sn=3ba7a6f7b836e4f74b1fb083c72838eb",
  "date": "2026-01-14 05:19:00",
  "author": " (沃垠AI)",
  "siteName": "沃垠AI",
  "content": "<html>\n <head></head>\n <body>\n  <p style=\"margin: 0px 8px 24px;line-height: 1.6em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">大家好，我是冷逸，你们的测评手替又上线了。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 0px 8px 24px;line-height: 1.6em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">今天，我想和大家聊一款昨晚刚刚发布的Real-time World Model——</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;font-weight: bold;\">PixVerse R1</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 0px 8px 24px;line-height: 1.6em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">我深度体验了一番，</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;font-weight: bold;\">这个模型还真的有点不太一样。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 0px 8px 24px;line-height: 1.6em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"line-height: 1.6em;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">它不是一款“生成得</span></span><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">更快”的视频模型（尽管速度上PixVerse早已没有对手），而是</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;font-weight: bold;\">从根本上改变了视频的生成方式和交互逻辑</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 0px 8px 24px;line-height: 1.6em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">给大家看个case，你就明白了。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 0px 8px 24px;line-height: 1.6em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">初始画面：一个人在冰雪世界中行走。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 0px 8px 8px;line-height: 1.6em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">你可以马上命令，让她跑得更快点。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-bottom: 16px;padding: 0.5em;\" data-mpa-action-id=\"mkcchmzd20pa\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img js_insertlocalimg\" data-ratio=\"0.9579124579124579\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"gif\" data-w=\"594\" style=\"box-shadow: rgb(210, 210, 210) 0px 0px 0.5em 0px;background-color: transparent;border-radius: 6px;height: auto !important;\" type=\"block\" data-imgfileid=\"506240415\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=4952b07a&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_gif%2FNX4HOlP6ibCicyupu9V0z91E1Kqz4hskbziasND9ZTdAatKISHFAicyapJtmmUlRtK82XKQ0NkIvZSmxEbSq9Hib0gQ%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dgif%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 0px 8px 8px;line-height: 1.6em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">也可以让画面中出现龙卷风</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 14px;letter-spacing: 1px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\">（别问为什么雪山上能见到龙卷风，就没有AI办不到的事情</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"1\" data-w=\"128\" style=\"display: inline-block;width: 20px;vertical-align: middle;background-size: cover;height: auto !important;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=510a64c9&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2FNX4HOlP6ibCice889lF3X0XVxplgYiaiblY1KWUme4eyNLuuebghVzvBNa2y0ADmEqvsX04G33EmkUW1u1sjQxM5pQ%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 14px;letter-spacing: 1px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\">）</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-bottom: 16px;padding: 0.5em;\" data-mpa-action-id=\"mkcci1gs1oz8\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img js_insertlocalimg\" data-ratio=\"0.9579124579124579\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"gif\" data-w=\"594\" style=\"box-shadow: rgb(210, 210, 210) 0px 0px 0.5em 0px;background-color: transparent;border-radius: 6px;height: auto !important;\" type=\"block\" data-imgfileid=\"506240420\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=59ccf17f&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_gif%2FNX4HOlP6ibCicyupu9V0z91E1Kqz4hskbzQcvvD97iccLAX61dibOdgTiaVN5FHkS1WYJ1YshDRwIzBic80HpZzNpafw%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dgif%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 0px 8px 24px;line-height: 1.6em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">整个过程非常丝滑、连贯。你的Prompt会立刻作用于画面本身，实时改变视频状态，生成一个</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;font-weight: bold;\">持续演化的视觉世界</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 0px 8px 8px;line-height: 1.6em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">完整演示录屏我放在这里了，一帧未剪。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 24px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 0px 8px 24px;line-height: 1.6em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">这和以往的AI视频生成模式完全不同：</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 0px 8px 24px;line-height: 1.6em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">以往的AI视频：</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;font-weight: bold;\">输入Prompt → 等待生成 → 得到一个固定的视频文件。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 0px 8px 24px;line-height: 1.6em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">而PixVerse R1让视频不再是一次性生成的“结果”，而是一个</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;font-weight: bold;\">可实时干预、持续演化的视觉世界。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.22833333333333333\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"jpeg\" data-w=\"600\" style=\"height: auto !important;\" type=\"block\" data-imgfileid=\"506236477\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=d2b71a2a&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_jpg%2FNX4HOlP6ibCicV1QppcudDqHNibe1FiaSiaXvic8DcjbZP6CtUD7nHjdLA0fB0eibP1sbkJBqTVafECcdFc416I0ia2VHw%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Djpeg%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 0px 8px 24px;line-height: 1.6em;text-align: center;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 18px;letter-spacing: 1px;color: rgb(210, 79, 240);font-weight: bold;\">一手体验</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 0px 8px 24px;line-height: 1.6em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">昨晚模型上线后，我深度玩了玩，给大家说下我的使用体验。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 0px 8px 24px;line-height: 1.6em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">体验地址是</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:1px;font-size:15px;\">realtime.pixverse.ai</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">，首次打开你会看到这样的提示：</span></span></p>\n  <blockquote>\n   <p><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight:bold;\">Visualize Your World in Real-time,Powered by PixVerse R1.</span></span></p>\n   <p><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\">通过PixVerse R1，实时生成你的世界。</span></span></p>\n  </blockquote>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 0px;margin-right: 0px;margin-bottom: 16px;padding: 0.5em;\" data-mpa-action-id=\"mkctx4y0iyb\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img js_insertlocalimg\" data-ratio=\"0.7231481481481481\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" style=\"box-shadow: rgb(210, 210, 210) 0px 0px 0.5em 0px;background-color: transparent;border-radius: 6px;height: auto !important;\" type=\"block\" data-imgfileid=\"506240422\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=e4896ade&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2FNX4HOlP6ibCicyupu9V0z91E1Kqz4hskbzGQ6uIC4AwGMnFiamnnyA7icEl2mzc0ciaNOVqJrNetCL2KmzVXKpTo9ag%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 0px 8px 8px;line-height: 1.6em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">点击「Start」，进入创作页面，可以自建主题或选择推荐主题。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-bottom: 16px;padding: 0.5em;\" data-mpa-action-id=\"mkctx8t7g1r\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img js_insertlocalimg\" data-ratio=\"0.3490740740740741\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" style=\"box-shadow: rgb(210, 210, 210) 0px 0px 0.5em 0px;background-color: transparent;border-radius: 6px;height: auto !important;\" type=\"block\" data-imgfileid=\"506240423\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=978dd474&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2FNX4HOlP6ibCicyupu9V0z91E1Kqz4hskbz0b3wbcqhibZ9Zia4qEmP6gFPpnqpFUiaVKwFYdnuPicWZO6DkDoZbPviavw%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 0px 8px 8px;line-height: 1.6em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">我们选择一个「War Thunder」主题。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-bottom: 16px;padding: 0.5em;\" data-mpa-action-id=\"mka2kha8b4h\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img js_insertlocalimg\" data-ratio=\"0.9183908045977012\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"870\" style=\"box-shadow: rgb(210, 210, 210) 0px 0px 0.5em 0px;background-color: transparent;border-radius: 6px;height: auto !important;\" type=\"block\" data-imgfileid=\"506240392\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=50202ecc&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2FNX4HOlP6ibC9qq3uicz7l36Tic2icUKeJhOSHcffibBbnUa5RlE1aX8fMj7QImuC9l68PN7QMyLPIBnn6QfxMyOMFeA%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 0px 8px 8px;line-height: 1.6em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">随后进入创作界面。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-bottom: 16px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img js_insertlocalimg\" data-ratio=\"0.700925925925926\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" style=\"height: auto !important;\" type=\"block\" data-imgfileid=\"506240393\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=65cd933d&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2FNX4HOlP6ibC9qq3uicz7l36Tic2icUKeJhOS1ZKDoV9A5vJ6I83qxwkNBPdRJJplOybatURGlB4Wp8OeUnnMJP8Kkw%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 0px 8px 24px;line-height: 1.6em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">这时候你会发现，它和所有传统AI视频工具的界面都不一样：</span></span></p>\n  <ul style=\"list-style-type: disc;\" class=\"list-paddingleft-1\">\n   <li>\n    <p style=\"margin: 0px 8px 8px;line-height: 1.6em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">中央画面区域始终在</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;font-weight: bold;\">实时生成、流式播放</span></span></p>\n   </li>\n   <li>\n    <p style=\"margin: 0px 8px 8px;line-height: 1.6em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">右上角是倒计时</span></span></p>\n   </li>\n   <li>\n    <p style=\"margin: 0px 8px 24px;line-height: 1.6em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">下方是你的Prompt输入区（支持语音）</span></span></p>\n   </li>\n  </ul>\n  <p style=\"margin: 0px 8px 8px;line-height: 1.6em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">你输入的每一句指令，都会立刻作用在当前世界上。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-bottom: 16px;padding: 0.5em;\" data-mpa-action-id=\"mka2kodhowe\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img js_insertlocalimg\" data-ratio=\"0.9902080783353733\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"gif\" data-w=\"817\" style=\"box-shadow: rgb(210, 210, 210) 0px 0px 0.5em 0px;background-color: transparent;border-radius: 6px;height: auto !important;\" type=\"block\" data-imgfileid=\"506240401\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=e2d48da0&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_gif%2FNX4HOlP6ibC9qq3uicz7l36Tic2icUKeJhOSlPRMQA5kvwWLONWicCDwViaKlKFatnkXLM6iaicib1vtEW63attSnLYFJ4Q%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dgif%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 0px 8px 8px;line-height: 1.6em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">我录制了一段操作过程，大家可以直观感受下。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-bottom: 16px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 0px 8px 24px;line-height: 1.6em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">这种体验非常新鲜。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 0px 8px 24px;line-height: 1.6em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">它不像传统AI视频：发一句Prompt，等一会儿，拿到一个镜头；</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 0px 8px 24px;line-height: 1.6em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">也不像3D模型：先生成一个静态世界，再让你进入；</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 0px 8px 24px;line-height: 1.6em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">更不像游戏：把一个“提前造好的世界”装进盒子里让你游玩。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 0px 8px 24px;line-height: 1.6em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;font-weight: bold;\">PixVerse-R1是在“边想，边造世界”。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 0px 8px 24px;line-height: 1.6em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">世界不是预制的，而是现炒的。一手，鲜活，且充满无限可能。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 0px 8px 24px;line-height: 1.6em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">所以说实话，我刚开始体验PixVerse R1，也没法立刻给它下一个准确的定义。但有一点我很确定，它不是现有任何一种媒体形态的简单延伸。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 0px 8px 24px;line-height: 1.6em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">它更像是一个全新的物种。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 0px 8px 24px;line-height: 1.6em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;font-weight: bold;\">一个可能会引领未来AI生成世界的全新媒介。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 0px 8px 8px;line-height: 1.6em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">特别值得一提的是，它也支持语音输入。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-bottom: 16px;padding: 0.5em;\" data-mpa-action-id=\"mka2l48124sq\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img js_insertlocalimg\" data-ratio=\"0.9136786188579017\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"753\" style=\"box-shadow: rgb(210, 210, 210) 0px 0px 0.5em 0px;background-color: transparent;border-radius: 6px;height: auto !important;\" type=\"block\" data-imgfileid=\"506240394\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=a6f18091&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2FNX4HOlP6ibC9qq3uicz7l36Tic2icUKeJhOS6hulbC4iaGVWInqibrj0Nz9cCRveiabNoYxEEib2fkr2ofb10cSkPiaLTIQ%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 0px 8px 24px;line-height: 1.6em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">大家都知道，键盘打字的速度，很难跟上实时生成的视频世界。一旦世界开始“跑起来”，语音输入的优势就非常明显。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 0px 8px 8px;line-height: 1.6em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">你可以用PixVerse内置的语音工具，也可以用第三方语音输入。我同样录了一个演示视频。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-bottom: 24px;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 0px 8px 8px;line-height: 1.6em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">目前这一版PixVerse R1，单次创作最长支持</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;font-weight: bold;\">5分钟</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 24px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 0px 8px 24px;line-height: 1.6em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">但我觉得，这一定不是它的终点。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 0px 8px 24px;line-height: 1.6em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">未来或许会实现无限时长，届时限制它的只能是</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;font-weight: bold;\">我们的想象力</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 0px 8px 8px;line-height: 1.6em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">当然，如果单纯看画面质量，比如清晰度、物理细节、镜头精度等，</span></span><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">它还不及PixVerse原始模型的效果，不像大家熟悉的AI视频的质感</span></span><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-bottom: 16px;padding: 0.5em;\" data-mpa-action-id=\"mkcw3kzeozu\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img js_insertlocalimg\" data-ratio=\"0.5796407185628742\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"gif\" data-w=\"835\" style=\"box-shadow: rgb(210, 210, 210) 0px 0px 0.5em 0px;background-color: transparent;border-radius: 6px;height: auto !important;\" type=\"block\" data-imgfileid=\"506240432\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=dea58f7f&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_gif%2FNX4HOlP6ibCicyupu9V0z91E1Kqz4hskbzmBjWs22VAc4ogy4cQhyQapl4n09ibQ5WtNiauPW8CSFmiaAdEUFHapibQA%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dgif%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 0px 8px 24px;line-height: 1.6em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">但PixVerse R1开启的，是一种</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;font-weight: bold;\">全新的交互范式</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">：</span></span></p>\n  <blockquote>\n   <p><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight:bold;\">Real-time、Playable Reality</span></span></p>\n  </blockquote>\n  <p style=\"margin: 0px 8px 24px;line-height: 1.6em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">在这里，用户不再只是使用者，而更像是一个共创者，甚至是世界的一部分。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 0px 8px 24px;line-height: 1.6em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;font-weight: bold;\">你不是在“生成视频”，而是在和一个平行世界持续对话。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 0px 8px 24px;line-height: 1.6em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">它不是AI视频，不是游戏，不是直播，也不是虚拟世界，而是一种可以</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;font-weight: bold;\">被“玩”的视频现实</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">（Playable Reality）。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 0px 8px 24px;line-height: 1.6em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">从这角度看，我感觉：PixVerse R1给整个行业扔下了一枚不太容易被立刻理解的炸弹。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 0px 8px 24px;line-height: 1.6em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">这也是为什么，这个Real-time World Model会被命名为</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;font-weight: bold;\">PixVerse R1</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.22833333333333333\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"jpeg\" data-w=\"600\" style=\"height: auto !important;\" type=\"block\" data-imgfileid=\"506236478\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=54b71409&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_jpg%2FNX4HOlP6ibCicV1QppcudDqHNibe1FiaSiaXvaAstRwhiayia3Y48FgMzdQ7LPRGS3mz0iaKmBic96xZwHoc195LUjDPUow%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Djpeg%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 0px 8px 24px;line-height: 1.6em;text-align: center;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 18px;letter-spacing: 1px;color: rgb(210, 79, 240);font-weight: bold;\">技术拆解</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 0px 8px 24px;line-height: 1.6em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">在模型发布的同时，PixVerse也公开了他们的技术论文：</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 0px 8px 24px;line-height: 1.6em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;font-weight: bold;\">《PixVerse-R1: Next-Generation Real-Time World Model》</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 0px 8px 24px;line-height: 1.6em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">核心目标只有一个：</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;font-weight: bold;\">把视频生成，从“离线片段”，变成“连续、可交互、实时响应的视觉流”。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 0px 8px 24px;line-height: 1.6em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">怎么做到的呢？简单来说由三部分构成：</span></span></p>\n  <blockquote>\n   <p style=\"margin-bottom: 24px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight:bold;\">Omni基座模型 + 无限流式生成架构 + 实时生成引擎</span></span></p>\n  </blockquote>\n  <p style=\"margin: 0px 8px 24px;line-height: 1.6em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">首先是</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;font-weight: bold;\">Omni基座模型</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 0px 8px 8px;line-height: 1.6em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">这是一个端到端的原生多模态模型，把文本、图像、视频、音频统一成连续的token流。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 24px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img js_insertlocalimg\" data-ratio=\"0.5472222222222223\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" style=\"height: auto !important;\" type=\"block\" data-imgfileid=\"506240421\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=a08db8a0&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2FNX4HOlP6ibCicyupu9V0z91E1Kqz4hskbzicjnOGAict3y8RqDJnTiaAJdkwGXjrn1qKRUTXvwzCL4ghQWqdgSXBauA%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 0px 8px 24px;line-height: 1.6em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">在训练阶段，它学习了大量真实世界的视频数据，因此具备生成复杂、长时间一致场景的能力——也就是我们直观感受到的“世界感”。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 0px 8px 24px;line-height: 1.6em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">初始画面：一位士兵趴在雪地里，用望远镜观察前方。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 0px 8px 8px;line-height: 1.6em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">一只乌鸦飞过。</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\">（绿色部分为提示词）</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-bottom: 16px;padding: 0.5em;\" data-mpa-action-id=\"mkctxj431ddx\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img js_insertlocalimg\" data-ratio=\"0.565625\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"gif\" data-w=\"640\" style=\"box-shadow: rgb(210, 210, 210) 0px 0px 0.5em 0px;background-color: transparent;border-radius: 6px;height: auto !important;\" type=\"block\" data-imgfileid=\"506240428\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=e94a0bc9&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_gif%2FNX4HOlP6ibCicyupu9V0z91E1Kqz4hskbztQKWLlhk8Y8MV028g2n0cicPSQicVRpAvkUNf51TbsbRO5kibMAFPiciazA%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dgif%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 0px 8px 8px;line-height: 1.6em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">巡逻队发现了士兵。他开始拼命逃跑。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-bottom: 16px;padding: 0.5em;\" data-mpa-action-id=\"mkctxmq41vbd\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img js_insertlocalimg\" data-ratio=\"0.5656213704994193\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"gif\" data-w=\"861\" style=\"box-shadow: rgb(210, 210, 210) 0px 0px 0.5em 0px;background-color: transparent;border-radius: 6px;height: auto !important;\" type=\"block\" data-imgfileid=\"506240429\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=6c794e02&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_gif%2FNX4HOlP6ibCicyupu9V0z91E1Kqz4hskbzicVCeXUwzSiaWZwB5prAVTbNABQlWdaFdTbSic7ync4xYzmicB2ibkgMMOg%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dgif%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 0px 8px 8px;line-height: 1.6em;\"><span data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">他跌倒在坦克旁边。</span></span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;padding: 0.5em;\" data-mpa-action-id=\"mkctxqedqdn\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img js_insertlocalimg\" data-ratio=\"0.565625\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"gif\" data-w=\"640\" style=\"box-shadow: rgb(210, 210, 210) 0px 0px 0.5em 0px;background-color: transparent;border-radius: 6px;height: auto !important;\" type=\"block\" data-imgfileid=\"506240430\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=5afbaca7&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_gif%2FNX4HOlP6ibCicyupu9V0z91E1Kqz4hskbz3BfZLNCq2AaSwec7JqdB7EXmp5XzHtBCXS1lV0k23clXe0u3icvcBpw%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dgif%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 0px 8px 8px;line-height: 1.6em;\"><span data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">飞机对坦克实施轰炸。</span></span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-bottom: 16px;padding: 0.5em;\" data-mpa-action-id=\"mkctxw8tb1\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img js_insertlocalimg\" data-ratio=\"0.5656213704994193\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"gif\" data-w=\"861\" style=\"box-shadow: rgb(210, 210, 210) 0px 0px 0.5em 0px;background-color: transparent;border-radius: 6px;height: auto !important;\" type=\"block\" data-imgfileid=\"506240431\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=282d5fb1&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_gif%2FNX4HOlP6ibCicyupu9V0z91E1Kqz4hskbzl2cD9bORIgZvtRELcPicY2GgDCZUvo6oTmV4v1W8k6dQwbFjQEiaGKCw%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dgif%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 0px 8px 8px;line-height: 1.6em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">整个镜头衔接非常自然，且遵循物理规律。完整的demo，我放在这里了。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 24px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 0px 8px 24px;line-height: 1.6em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">第二个关键点，是生成机制。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 0px 8px 8px;line-height: 1.6em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">PixVerse R1采用的是</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;font-weight: bold;\">自回归生成</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">，而非传统扩散模型那种“先算完整片段”的方式。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img js_insertlocalimg\" data-ratio=\"0.562962962962963\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" style=\"height: auto !important;\" type=\"block\" data-imgfileid=\"506240403\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=543b0650&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2FNX4HOlP6ibC9qq3uicz7l36Tic2icUKeJhOS2TyTfsLxl9icMq8sZ072oTN49fLgaC1wVSTapjp6LYUicnyaJYG1QTdA%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 0px 8px 24px;line-height: 1.6em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">这意味着，它可以持续生成、无限延展视觉流，而不是只能吐出一个固定长度的视频。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 0px 8px 24px;line-height: 1.6em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">最后，也是PixVerse的传统强项——</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;font-weight: bold;\">速度</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 0px 8px 8px;line-height: 1.6em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">在PixVerse R1中，他们重新设计了</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;font-weight: bold;font-style: normal;\">实时生成引擎</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">，把传统视频生成中动辄几十步的采样过程，压缩到了1–4步。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img js_insertlocalimg\" data-ratio=\"0.562962962962963\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" style=\"height: auto !important;\" type=\"block\" data-imgfileid=\"506240408\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=5209140b&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2FNX4HOlP6ibC9qq3uicz7l36Tic2icUKeJhOSwSFZ3ND2sYPRvTICDh8bgR1xsFccRYR3FbNjnFnULORxo3jdHNcJsg%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 0px 8px 24px;line-height: 1.6em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">所以，我们能看到近乎实时响应的画面变化。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.20666666666666667\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"jpeg\" data-w=\"600\" style=\"height: auto !important;\" type=\"block\" data-imgfileid=\"506236476\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=616247c5&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_jpg%2FNX4HOlP6ibCicV1QppcudDqHNibe1FiaSiaXvchrPAK3S9ibJjY6ibrzfXP6eUeh1IhG5DzGiaatTn9k3XGl1vebRJm43Q%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Djpeg%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 0px 8px 24px;line-height: 1.6em;text-align: center;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 18px;letter-spacing: 1px;color: rgb(210, 79, 240);font-weight: bold;\">写在最后</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 0px 8px 24px;line-height: 1.6em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">整个体验下来，我的感觉是：PixVerse R1让实时、长时序的AI生成世界第一次变得可行。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 0px 8px 24px;line-height: 1.6em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">这不仅是视频媒介的一次演进，更是一次从「生成内容」走向「生成世界」的跃迁。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 0px 8px 24px;line-height: 1.6em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">它的意义在于，</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;font-weight: bold;\">把「世界模型」从离线想象，推进到了实时生成、即时响应、长时一致的阶段。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 0px 8px 24px;line-height: 1.6em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">每一次用户输入，不只是剪辑点，而是一次对世界状态的干预；每一帧画面，也不只是结果，而是下一步推理的上下文。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 0px 8px 24px;line-height: 1.6em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">一旦这样的世界可以被反复运行、被规模化调用、被Agent接管，游戏、仿真、训练、创作，甚至现实决策的预演，都会在同一条技术线上融合。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 0px 8px 24px;line-height: 1.6em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">所以，这并不是“视频生成更快了”。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 0px 8px 24px;line-height: 1.6em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">而是：</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;font-weight: bold;\">AI，第一次开始拥有一个可以长期存在的世界。</span></span></p>\n </body>\n</html>",
  "aiSummary": "PixVerse R1 是一款颠覆性的实时世界模型，首次实现视频的实时交互与持续演化，将 AI 生成从“内容”推向“世界”，开启了“可玩的视频现实”新范式。",
  "oneSentenceSummary": "PixVerse R1 是一款颠覆性的实时世界模型，首次实现视频的实时交互与持续演化，将 AI 生成从“内容”推向“世界”，开启了“可玩的视频现实”新范式。",
  "summary": "文章深入评测了 PixVerse R1 这款实时世界模型，指出其根本性改变了现有视频生成和交互逻辑。与传统 AI 视频一次性生成固定文件不同，PixVerse R1 实现了视频的实时干预、持续演化，用户可以像与一个平行世界对话一样，实时修改视频内容。作者通过实际操作演示了其丝滑、连贯的交互体验，并将其定义为一种“可玩的视频现实”（Playable Reality）。技术拆解部分介绍了 PixVerse R1 的核心构成：Omni 基座模型、无限流式生成架构和实时生成引擎，强调其将“世界模型”从离线想象推向实时生成、即时响应、长时一致的阶段。文章认为 PixVerse R1 不仅是视频媒介的演进，更是从“生成内容”到“生成世界”的跃迁，具有深远的行业影响。",
